data.description: Welcome to 3266 McCoy Road! This custom single story home sits on one acre- perfect size for a hobby farm! You'll love the updated kitchen which boasts stainless steel appliances, new flooring and quartz counter tops. Great room concept allows for easy entertaining or simply relaxing by the wood burning stove. Updated bathrooms offers new flooring and vanities. Indoor laundry room is a plus! Don't miss the the spacious outdoor area which allows for gardening, entertaining, RV parking and so much more. Owned solar is an added bonus!
